data.description: Gorgeous single-story home, located in Heritage Lake Community.  Nestled at the end of the cul-de-sac, and a private reserve to the left.   There are 3 bedrooms, a den and 2 full and one guest baths.  The large open concept space has lots of natural light.  The entertainment friendly kitchen features a large 4 seat, granite countertop.  The beautiful double glass sliding patio doors lead out to the large, landscaped backyard with covered patio.  This home is move-in ready and a clean slate to create and make this Your home.
